<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="216">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$xiexienidemeihao" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/xiexienidemeihao" class="zg-link" title="王山儿">王山儿</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$wang-jie-51" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/wang-jie-51" class="zg-link" title="王杰">王杰</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$zhu-zi-pei-14" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/zhu-zi-pei-14" class="zg-link" title="祝子佩">祝子佩</a></span>
